ersymmetric versions of these solutions have interesting\nimplications for the spectrum of supersymmetric states in, e.g. ${\\cal N}=4$\nYang-Mills theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 18:00:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
