icantly\ndifferent from that of the bulk of the ejecta of the respective element, thus\ngiving blueshifted lines for bulk receding material, and vice versa. We compare\nthe 3.3 $M_\\odot$ He-core model to observations of the Type Ib supernova SN\n2007Y.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 18:11:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-31"}
