iments with various machine\nlearning architectures and datasets to evaluate our proposed framework, such as\nMNIST and CIFAR-10.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 03:34:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 May 2023 11:54:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-19"}
