nic properties under the effect\nof minimal strain and twist for different chalcogen-based TMDs, and it shows\nthe band gap tunability from direct to indirect due to interlayer interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 06:59:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
