ously\nwork which trying to understand the magnetic phase transition in Ca3Ru2O7, such\nas neutron scattering, specific heat, and other advanced transport\nmeasurements, our work provides a more convenient yet efficient method, which\nmay also find applications in other correlated spin materials in general.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 10:59:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
