 PARADISE simulation\nand in-situ measurements of $\\lesssim 5$ MeV ions is obtained. Our modelling\nshows that the intricate intensity variations observed at both ACE and Bepi\nwere influenced by the non-uniform emission of energetic particles from the\ndeformed shock wave and demonstrates the influence of even modest background\nsolar wind structures on the development of SEP events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 15:19:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
