f how the behavior of the\nhost star is responsible for how we observe exoplanet characteristics, most\nnotably their radii and atmospheric properties, and how the activity may alter\nour measurements or impact the evolution of planetary properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 18:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-18"}
